subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Lindsay Davenport won her 55th career WTA title by overpowering Olga Govortsova, 6-2, 6-1, in the final of the Cellular South Cup in Memphis. Davenport, who was seeded fourth, needed slightly more than an hour to beat the fifth-seeded Govortsova and improve her match record to 13-2 this season.
